{"id":"Aldrete_score.v0.0.3","gdl_version":"2.0","concept":"gt0001","language":{"original_language":"ISO_639-1::en"},"description":{"original_author":{"name":"Umiah Gohar","email":"umiah.gohar@cambio.se","organisation":"Cambio CDS","date":"2024-12-24"},"lifecycle_state":"Author draft","details":{"en":{"id":"en","copyright":"© Cambio CDS","keywords":["Aldrete","score","recovery","anesthesia","PACU","post-anesthesia","care","unit","discharge"],"purpose":"To calculate the total sum for the Aldrete score to assess the anesthesia recovery phases and patient readiness to be discharged from PACU.","use":"<p>Use to evaluate the recovery of patients after anesthesia and their readiness to be discharged from PACU. The score is calculated by adding the points of the individual variables:</p><p><strong>Variables</strong>:</p><table><thead><tr style=\"text-align: left;\"><th>Variable</th><th>Answers</th><th>Points</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr style=\"text-align: left;\"><td rowspan=\"3\">Consciousness</td><td>Fully awake</td><td>2</td></tr><tr style=\"text-align: left;\"><td>Arousable</td><td>1</td></tr><tr style=\"text-align: left;\"><td>Not responding</td><td>0</td></tr><tr style=\"text-align: left;\"><td rowspan=\"3\">Mobility – on command</td><td>Able to move four extremities</td><td>2</td></tr><tr style=\"text-align: left;\"><td>Able to move two extremities</td><td>1</td></tr><tr style=\"text-align: left;\"><td>Able to move 0 extremities</td><td>0</td></tr><tr style=\"text-align: left;\"><td rowspan=\"3\">Breathing</td><td>Able to breathe deeply</td><td>2</td></tr><tr style=\"text-align: left;\"><td>Dyspnea</td><td>1</td></tr><tr style=\"text-align: left;\"><td>Apnea</td><td>0</td></tr><tr style=\"text-align: left;\"><td rowspan=\"3\">Circulation</td><td>Systemic BP ≠ 20% of the preanesthetic level</td><td>2</td></tr><tr style=\"text-align: left;\"><td>Systemic BP between 20% and 49% of the preanesthetic level</td><td>1</td></tr><tr style=\"text-align: left;\"><td>Systemic BP ≠ 50% of the preanesthetic level</td><td>0</td></tr><tr style=\"text-align: left;\"><td rowspan=\"3\">Color</td><td>Normal</td><td>2</td></tr><tr style=\"text-align: left;\"><td>Pale, jaundiced, blotchy</td><td>1</td></tr><tr style=\"text-align: left;\"><td>Cyanotic</td><td>0</td></tr></tbody></table><p>The evaluation occurs immediately after surgery and then every 1 hour before the patient is deemed as ready for discharge.</p>"}},"other_details":{"references":"Aldrete JA, Kroulik D. A postanesthetic recovery score. Anesth Analg. 1970 Nov-Dec;49(6):924-34. PMID: 5534693.","en":"To evaluate recovery after anesthesia and patient readiness to be discharged from PACU."},"other_contributors":[]},"definition":{"data_bindings":{"gt0002":{"id":"gt0002","type":"INPUT","model_id":"openEHR-EHR-OBSERVATION.aldrete.v0","template_id":"openEHR-EHR-OBSERVATION.aldrete.v0","elements":{"gt0003":{"id":"gt0003","path":"/data[at0001]/events[at0002]/data[at0003]/items[at0004]/items[at0005]"},"gt0004":{"id":"gt0004","path":"/data[at0001]/events[at0002]/data[at0003]/items[at0004]/items[at0009]"},"gt0005":{"id":"gt0005","path":"/data[at0001]/events[at0002]/data[at0003]/items[at0004]/items[at0013]"},"gt0006":{"id":"gt0006","path":"/data[at0001]/events[at0002]/data[at0003]/items[at0004]/items[at0017]"},"gt0007":{"id":"gt0007","path":"/data[at0001]/events[at0002]/data[at0003]/items[at0004]/items[at0021]"}}},"gt0008":{"id":"gt0008","type":"OUTPUT","model_id":"openEHR-EHR-OBSERVATION.aldrete.v0","template_id":"openEHR-EHR-OBSERVATION.aldrete.v0","elements":{"gt0009":{"id":"gt0009","path":"/data[at0001]/events[at0002]/data[at0003]/items[at0025]"}}},"gt0010":{"id":"gt0010","type":"OUTPUT","model_id":"openEHR-EHR-EVALUATION.aldrete_score_assessment.v0","template_id":"openEHR-EHR-EVALUATION.aldrete_score_assessment.v0","elements":{"gt0011":{"id":"gt0011","path":"/data[at0001]/items[at0002]"}}}},"templates":{},"rules":{"gt0012":{"id":"gt0012","priority":3,"then":["$gt0009|Total score| = $gt0003|Con